choices.text: Little Frane is already in tenth grade, but is still struggling with Pascal in computer class. For homework, his teacher wrote the following program into his notebook, and he needs to determine the output, given the integer $N$. readln(N); counter := 0; for i := N - 1 downto 1 do begin   counter := counter + 1;   if N mod i = 0 then break; end; writeln(counter); Write a program which solves Frane s problem.
